	(25, 1, 0, 'modal', '', 0, 5, 0, '<div id="thank" class="modal fade" tabindex="-1" role="dialog">\n      <div class="modal-dialog">\n        <div class="modal-content">\n          <div class="modal-header">\n            <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal"><i class="fa fa-times"></i></button>\n            <span class="modal-title">Спасибо!</span>\n          </div>\n          <div class="modal-body">\n            <strong class="title">Ваша заявка успешно отправлена</strong>\n            <p>Наши представители связутся с вами в ближайшее время</p>\n            <span class="btn btn_green" data-dismiss="modal">OK</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div id="call_you" class="modal fade" tabindex="-1" role="dialog">\n      <div class="modal-dialog">\n        <div class="modal-content">\n          <div class="modal-header">\n            <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal"><i class="fa fa-times"></i></button>\n            <span class="modal-title">Вам перезвонить?</span>\n          </div>\n          <div class="modal-body">\n            <p>Оставьте свой номер телефона, и мы Вам перезвоним</p>\n			[[!FormIt?\n              &hooks=`email,redirect`\n              &emailTpl=`email_tpl`\n              &emailTo=`melina.antipova@gmail.com`\n              &redirectTo=`14`\n              &validate=`name:required,phone:isNumber:required`\n           ]]\n            <div class="form">\n              <form class="contact js_validate" method="post" action=""[[~[[*id]]]]"">\n                <div class="form-group col-xs-12">\n                  <label for="name" class="label">Имя*</label>\n                  <input type="text" class="form-control" name="name" id="name" required />\n                  <span class="success form-control-feedback">[[+fi.error.name]]</span>\n                  <div class="error_text"><i class="form-control-feedback"></i></div>\n                </div>\n                <div class="form-gro